Kafka Steps
===========
Link:: https://javatute.com/kafka/spring-boot-kafka-producer-and-consumer-example-step-by-step-guide/
How to install Apache Kafka.
How to start zookeeper/kafka and create a topic.
How to configure spring and apache Kafka.
How to create Kafka producer and consumer to send/receive string messages – Hello word example.
How to create Kafka producer and consumer to send/receive JSON messages.
How to create a Kafka Consumer Rest controller/end-point.
Testing using postman.
======================================================================================================
1)Download and install Apache Kafka
	https://kafka.apache.org/downloads
2)command to run zookeeper
==>.\bin\windows\zookeeper-server-start.bat .\config\zookeeper.properties
3)command to run kafka
==>.\bin\windows\kafka-server-start.bat .\config\server.properties
4)creating topic (topicName=message-events-topic-1)
==>.\bin\windows\kafka-topics.bat –create –zookeeper localhost:2181 –replication-factor 1 –partitions 1 –topic message-events-topic-1
5)Write your applications
======================================================================================================
